# QA Manual Testing Project – SauceDemo

This repository contains a small manual testing project created as part of my practice in software testing.

The project demonstrates basic QA activities such as:

- creating test cases
- executing manual tests
- identifying and documenting bugs
- preparing basic testing documentation

## Tested application
https://www.saucedemo.com/

## Project structure

README.md – project description  
SauceDemo_Manual_Testing_Project.xlsx – test cases and execution results  
bug-report.md – documented bug discovered during testing  
Test Summary – testing overview and results  

## Testing scope

The following areas were tested:

- Login functionality
- Product listing
- Add to cart / remove from cart
- Basic navigation

## Tools used

- Manual testing
- Excel
- GitHub

